Package com.example.chaosruler.msa_manager.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    encryption
    a Singleton object (only one instance in runtime) responsible for encryptiing and decrypting data stored in local database and local android machine AES 256bit was chosen for encryption protocol
    global_variables_dataclass
    a Singleton like objec that holds data true across all the activities such as settings and databases along with functions usabele across activities
    offline_mode_service
    service responsible for storing server commands offline and sending them whenever possible
    remote_SQL_Helper
    a singleton object that connects us to the database and sends queries to it responsible for all the remote commands
    themer
    general static class responsible for getting the right updated theme for every page based on the settings of the style chosen by the user, default being Light
